targets.expr:
{log_type="application", k8s_container_name="authorino" }
      | json
      | line_format "{{.message}}"
      | json
      | msg = "evaluating for input"
      | label_format username = input_auth_identity_user_username, request = input_context_request_http_id, model_name = input_context_request_http_headers_kserve_isvc_name
      | username != "" and request != "" and model_name="$model_name"

{ log_type="application", k8s_container_name=~"kserve-container" } |= `chatcmpl` | json | line_format "{{.message}}" |~ "prompt" | label_format model_name="{{.kubernetes_annotations_openshift_io_display_name}}" | model_name="$model_name" | regexp "chatcmpl-(?<request>.*?):" | regexp "prompt: \"(?<prompt>.*?)\", "

{ log_type="application", k8s_container_name=~"kserve-container" } |= `chatcmpl` | json | line_format "{{.message}}" |~ "Prompt.*Total" | regexp "chatcmpl-(?<request>.*?)," | regexp "Prompt: (?<prompt>.*?), " | regexp "Completion: (?<completion>.*?), " | regexp "Total: (?<total>.*?)$"

sum by (username) (
  count_over_time(
    { log_type="application", k8s_container_name="authorino" }
      | json
      | line_format "{{.message}}"
      | json
      | msg = "evaluating for input"
      | label_format username = input_auth_identity_user_username, request_id = input_context_request_http_id, model_name = input_context_request_http_headers_kserve_isvc_name
      | username != "" and request_id != "" and model_name="$model_name"
    [$interval]
  )
)
